games.description: Statsify supports the majority of games offered on Hypixel. To check your stats in a game run `/[game]`. For example you can run `/bedwars` to check your BedWars stats.
games.title: Games

historical.description: Statsify lets you check your daily, weekly, and monthly stats through `/daily`, `/weekly` and `/monthly`. If you missed a reset you can view them by running `/yesterday`, `/lastweek`, and `/lastmonth`.
historical.title: Historical

leaderboards.description: Statsify offers thousands of leaderboards through the `/leaderboard` command. Run `/leaderboard`, then pick the gamemode, and pick a leaderboard to view. You can hit the search button to search for a specific player or position. You can also hit the up and down buttons to view more pages.
leaderboards.title: Leaderboards

minecraft.description: You can view general Minecraft information such as skins, UUIDs, capes through `/skin`, `/uuid`, and `/cape` respectively. Statsify also has commands to generate Minecraft text through `/text`. View Minecraft colors through `/colors` and preview Minecraft servers through `/server`.
minecraft.title: Minecraft

If you want to be able to reset at a specific time check out $t(socials.premium).
